(286, 177, 'Cleaning', 'Dental cleaning is especially beneficial in prevention of oral health problems. Dental cleanings are recommended every six months. Regular dental cleaning keeps teeth free from plaque build-up and stops oral problems before they become a real problem. A cleaning is generally accompanied by a complete oral examination, including X-rays to get an understandable visual view of overall oral health.<br>', '1450799561untitled-1.jpg'),
